					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">‚ö° Key Technologies</h3>
						<ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
							<li>‚Ä¢ IoT sensors for real-time monitoring</li>
							<li>‚Ä¢ JIBCHAIN L1 blockchain integration</li>
